---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Oregon Motorcycle Rental, Off Road Trail Riding Enduro Tours, and Training"
  description="At Oregon Motorcycle Rental we rent Husqvarna and KTM off road enduro trail bikes and ride the best off road single track trails in Oregon and Washington"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Hood River, Oregon</p>
      <h1 class="display hero-title">Oregon Motorcycle Rental</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">We rent Husqvarna and KTM motorcycles and ride the best singletrack trails in Oregon and Southern Washington.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/motorcycle-rental-portland/" class="btn btn-big">View Bikes</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-big">Book a Ride</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <h2 class="display service-title">Bikes For Rent</h2>
          <p>Check out our range of KTM and Husqvarna dirt bikes. We have 150, 250, and 300 2-strokes, and 350 and 450 4-stroke motorcycles to choose from.</p>
          <a href="/motorcycle-rental-portland/" class="btn">View Bikes</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h2 class="display service-title">Training</h2>
          <p>Add $50 per rider per day for expert feedback and practice drills while on your ride. All levels welcome, including beginners and kids 12+.</p>
          <a href="/off-road-motorcycle-training/" class="btn">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h2 class="display service-title">Guided Locations</h2>
          <p>Ride Hood River, Coastal Oregon, Washington State, and Arizona. Year-round availability at our Oregon and Arizona locations.</p>
          <a href="/tour-packages-motorcycle-rides-oregon/" class="btn">See Locations</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="section-label">Make a Reservation</p>
      <h2 class="display section-title">Ready to ride?</h2>
      <p>Call Doug at <a href="tel:5092810156">509-281-0156</a> or use our contact form.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-big" style="margin-top:24px">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 80px 0 100px;
  }
  .hero-title { font-size: clamp(52px, 9vw, 110px); color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 22px; max-width: 620px; margin-bottom: 40px; opacity: 0.85; }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .services { padding: 80px 0; }
  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; }
  .service-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .service-title { font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px); color: var(--leather); }

  .cta-band { background: var(--cream-deep); padding: 80px 0; }
  .cta-band a[href^="tel"] { color: var(--rust); font-weight: 700; }
</style>
